item.title: car-trivia
item.description: car-trivia is a simple web app that pulls trivia questions from Open Trivia DB. You can test the game by going to https://car-trivia.herokuapp.com/.

item.title: MOHarvester
item.description: MOHarvester is a project to analyze the waterfowl data collected from the Missouri Department of Conservation. The data is collected each day of the hunting season from each of the 15 different hunting zones.
